  <brief_title>Assessment of Small Bowel Healing in Crohn's Disease Patients Treated With Cimzia Using Wireless Capsule Endoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Label Investigator Initiated, Single Site Study of Mucosal Healing in Patients With Small Bowel Crohn's Disease Treated With Certolizumab Pegol (Cimzia) Assessed by Wireless Capsule Endoscopy</official_title>
