  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Wireless Capsule Endoscopy has been the most reliable diagnostic standard for small bowel
      Crohn's disease. Endoscopic healing is an important endpoint to measure response to
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
